         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Aurelius Achilles (...) and however he is styled through M..., his agent, from N.N., (...) his mother being Ta... of my own free will I undertake to lease from you (...) dating from the present (...) year (...) the holdings belonging to you at the village Tholthis (..) from another or other parcels (...) previously cultivated by me (to sow annually) the one half (with) ......, the other half (to plant with .... the seed and .... at an annual rent of) ..... artabas of wheat.</ab>
